    "In most existing literature, messages are viewed as additional observations.",
    "Agents take messages as extra input to a policy function, a value function, or both.",
    "Thus, in the dimension of inner integration, we classify recent works into categories based on the learning model that is used to integrate messages.",
    "These categories are summarized in Table 8.",
    "Policy-levelBy exploiting information from other agents, each agent will no longer act independently."
